long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Allows open Azure DevOps workitems quickly

Click to the AzDo Quick Access button or press Ctrl+Shift+X.
Enter AzDo workitem id.
If there is a workitem id in a clipboard, it will be pasted in the popup input field.
Then press Enter or click the link.
You can also click on any recently opened workitem link.
